(To be cited as: "Hichem Rami Ait-El-Hara" or "Ait-El-Hara, Hichem Rami")

PhD, Formal Methods R&D Engineer at [OCamlPro](https://ocamlpro.com/), interested in SMT solving, constraint programming, symbolic execution and deductive verification.

## Professional experience

- R&D Engineer at [OCamlPro](https://ocamlpro.com/), since Sep 2021.
- PhD Student at [Université Paris-Saclay, CEA, List](https://list.cea.fr/en/), from Sep 2022 to Oct 2025.
- R&D Intern at [OCamlPro](https://ocamlpro.com/), from Mar 2021 to Sep 2021.

